<title>USA: Mississippi Valley increases repurchases.</title>
<headline>Mississippi Valley increases repurchases.</headline>
<dateline>ST. LOUIS 1997-04-17</dateline>
<text>
<p>Mississippi Valley Bancshares Inc said it is extending its April 18 authorization to repurchase shares of common stock and increase the maximum number of shares which may be repurchased to 400,000 or about 8.4 percent of outstanding shares.</p>
<p>It said no stock has been repurchased under the board's prior authorization.</p>
<p>The company said it may make these repurchases from time to time in the open market or in private transactions, depending upon market conditions, over the next 12 months.</p>
